Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dr. Tenma, this is not your fault."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"You only did\Nwhat you're supposed to do as a doctor."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"You didn't do anything wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please have the sandwich."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Then try to get some sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"You have to stay alive."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please save as many people as you can."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nina Fortner."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to kill him once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was I who brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved that monster…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are several blood vessels\Nin this arteriovenous malformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We will cut all the inflow arteries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and work on the outflow arteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Extraction of the nidus is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that went well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing.\NThe clipping was done very quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though that was your first surgery\Nsince your sabbatical,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,your gift seems greater than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great, Kenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about me.\NIt's news about your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's all because you did\Nthe perfect surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as one of Father's team members.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he appreciates that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one getting the hospital\Nsuch great recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of your father
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can work in Germany like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be okay if you just\Nfollow Father's lead and do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time before\Nhe becomes board chairman at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will soon be Chief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, you'll be the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the Director's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not built for a hard life,\Nso you'd better make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go out or…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sir! The lady is sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't take up a lot of her time.\NI'll leave as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come back after you've made\Nan appointment to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a policeman here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Ms. Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I investigated your father's\Nmurder nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lunge from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge? Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go now, Holss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that bungling policeman\Nwho couldn't solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after your father's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still able to afford this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, the furnishings have become\Neven more extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come to see how much I've made
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,from my father's inheritance\Nand the alimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I am doing quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see anything you like,\Nyou're welcome to take it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have my drinks,\Nthat is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here today because I have\Nsomething I need to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recall having seen this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not remember it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as it's from nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Its pattern is simple, but the design\Nis very intricate if you look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very fine item.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This tie gave me a hard time\Nsince it's from nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I was lucky that this tie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was a limited edition,\Nmade specially for frequent customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In the list of frequent customers,\NI found your name in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you purchase this tie and give it\Nto someone as a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This tie is an important key\Nto a certain murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought so many presents for so many men,\Nso I don't remember every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, all the men chasing me\Nwere only after my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All the men are gold diggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No one truly loved me from the bottom\Nof his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I robbed them all\Nwith divorce settlements!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of them. Serves them right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want something too? Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It will cost you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will come back again. Please contact me\Nif you think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring a bottle of whisky\Nthe next time you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva, can you talk to your father for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I only followed the order\Nof the patients coming in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to do the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the engagement ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Norden! Nice suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more beautiful than ever tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Holss! Get the car ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Hess.\NI see you've gotten a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be able\Nto leave the hospital this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter's wedding is next month.\NDo you think I can make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure you take it easy\Nat the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I was going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still go, all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all because of your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have you as a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can probably live long enough to see\Neven my grandchild's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly an amazing doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep working at this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Dr. Tenma. You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am about to see other patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell them I'm unavailable?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, are you in bed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Eva…\N-Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's tough but hang in there--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring my father back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lose some weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you took a sabbatical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. You should take\Na rest from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a workaholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost some weight too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spring now… Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In spring ten years ago,\Nwe used to go driving a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,At around this time,\Nyou tried to go swimming in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I panicked and stopped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva, I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get back with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After three failed marriages,\NI have finally realized this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only one person who has\Never truly loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you, Kenzo. Only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy you feel that way about me,\Nbut I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kenzo! I didn't tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The police came and asked\Nabout your necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something bad with that tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you that tie as a present.\NI'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do as I say,\NI'll stay quiet about the tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell the police about the necktie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That my father and the other doctors\Nwere killed nine years ago because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me Dr. Tenma as a material witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But, it's still…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough evidence\Nfor the Fortners and Maurer murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the murder at Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to solve a lot of\Ncases from this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Resignation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me\Nfor my selfishness, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been some weird rumors\Nabout you lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't believe any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you reconsider…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Yes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is a murder suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seal all the entrances to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't forget about the back exit.\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong over there? Look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But… Inspector…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us pass!\NYou're obstructing police work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dr. Tenma would never kill anyone!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The police should go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of police cars, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you just drop me off at the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still so busy, huh? Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another surgery to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Hold on. I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a doctor, just a money-grubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A man like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The twins… We can't find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Doctor. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you already forgotten\Nabout those twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me, Doctor!\NI don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to have died back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one\Nwho brought me back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,FIVE MONTHS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be another hot day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hot when you wear\Nso many clothes during the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:22:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Isn't it the newspaper\Nfrom three days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's a couple from Verden?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They said the murderer was a doctor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that you're\Ngoing to Verden too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if I'll get to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to find out.
